---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = "19 March 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How ashmo.io collects, uses, and protects your personal data."
>
  <section class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 pt-8 md:pt-16 pb-20 md:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-[720px]">

      <p class="text-xs text-text-tertiary uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-tertiary mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-10 text-text font-light leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>This website, <strong>ashmo.io</strong>, is operated by <strong>Ashraf Hassan</strong> ("Ashmo"), based in Dubai, United Arab Emirates. For any privacy-related matters, you can contact me at <a href="mailto:hello@ashmo.io" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@ashmo.io</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We collect two categories of data:</p>
          <p class="mb-2"><strong>Analytics data (automatic)</strong> — When you visit this site, Google Analytics 4 (via Google Tag Manager) automatically collects:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4">
            <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
            <li>General geographic location (country/city level)</li>
            <li>Device type, browser, and operating system</li>
            <li>Referral source (how you found this site)</li>
            <li>Scroll depth, outbound clicks, and file downloads</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-2"><strong>Contact form data (voluntary)</strong> — If you submit the contact form, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Your email address</li>
            <li>Your message</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Analytics data</strong> is used solely to understand how visitors use this site and to improve the content and experience. It is never sold or shared with third parties for marketing.</li>
            <li><strong>Contact form data</strong> is used only to respond to your enquiry. It is not added to any mailing list without your explicit consent.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">4. Google Analytics & Google Tag Manager</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">This site uses <strong>Google Analytics 4 (GA4)</strong> and <strong>Google Tag Manager</strong>, services provided by Google LLC. Google acts as a data processor on our behalf.</p>
          <p class="mb-4">We have also enabled <strong>Google Signals</strong>, which allows Google to associate your visit with your Google account (if you are signed in and have personalised ads enabled). This enables cross-device reporting and more accurate audience insights.</p>
          <p class="mb-4">Google may transfer and process data in the United States and other countries. For more information, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
          <p>You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">This site uses cookies placed by Google Analytics to distinguish unique visitors and sessions. These are first-party analytics cookies. We do not use advertising cookies, social tracking cookies, or any third-party marketing cookies.</p>
          <p>You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">6. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">If you are located in the European Economic Area, we process your data under the following legal bases:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> — for analytics, to understand and improve this site.</li>
            <li><strong>Contractual necessity</strong> — for contact form responses, to reply to your enquiry.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">7. UAE Personal Data Protection Law (PDPL)</h2>
          <p>As a UAE-based operator, we comply with Federal Decree-Law No. 45 of 2021 on the Protection of Personal Data. Data collected is limited to what is necessary, retained only for as long as required, and protected with appropriate security measures. You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal data by contacting us at <a href="mailto:hello@ashmo.io" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@ashmo.io</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Regardless of your location, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing</li>
            <li>Opt out of Google Signals / analytics tracking</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@ashmo.io" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@ashmo.io</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">9. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>Analytics event data is retained for 14 months. Contact form submissions are retained for as long as necessary to fulfill your request or as required by applicable law.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">10. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>This site contains links to external websites (LinkedIn, Instagram, YouTube, etc.). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their respective privacy policies.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page reflects when the most recent changes were made. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">12. Contact</h2>
          <p>For any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, contact: <a href="mailto:hello@ashmo.io" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@ashmo.io</a></p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
